data.description: 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath in Minneapolis neighborhood. Cute home with tons of potential. You'll be close to schools, 2 parks with play areas, shopping, dining, trails and the bus line. There is also easy access to the freeway so you'll have easy access to downtown Minneapolis, the Lakes, the airport and Mall of America. You're going to love this home!
